original_title: Johnny Rapid: 5 Years In The Making
overview: Five Years in the Making is a compilation of some of the superstar's best scenes, including when Johnny and Paddy O'Brian finally meet for the five year anniversary of MEN.com. Jake Bass and Cameron Kincade are just a few of the other soaking hot men you'll see taking advantage of Johnny. A compilation of muscle and talent cum together in this epic collection of top scenes that are sure to make you shout for more.
